{"id":28015310649,"name":"Test","node_id":"WFR_kwLOA_1uaM8AAAAGhde3OQ","head_branch":"fix/oug-indicator-npe_2.42","head_sha":"957c053126bc4ecc25dba96679ca1091601a5682","path":".github/workflows/run-tests.yml","run_number":54310,"run_attempt":1,"event":"pull_request","display_title":"backport: fix: resolve OUG{} indicator count to zero when org unit has no group members","status":"completed","conclusion":"success","workflow_id":10954,"check_suite_id":75535656465,"check_suite_node_id":"CS_kwDOA_1uaM8AAAARlkamEQ","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/28015310649","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/28015310649","created_at":"2026-06-23T09:10:10Z","updated_at":"2026-06-23T09:24:44Z","run_started_at":"2026-06-23T09:10:10Z","jobs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/28015310649/jobs","logs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/28015310649/logs","check_suite_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/check-suites/75535656465","artifacts_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/28015310649/artifacts","cancel_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/28015310649/cancel","rerun_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/28015310649/rerun","head_commit":{"message":"fix: resolve OUG{} indicator count to zero when org unit has no group members (#24266)\n\nItemOrgUnitGroupCount.evaluate read visitor.getParams().getOrgUnitCountMap()\nunguarded. In the analytics indicator path (DataHandler.getIndicatorValue), the\nper-org-unit target count map is null when the org unit target aggregation\nreturns no row for an org unit — i.e. when that org unit's subtree contains no\nmembers of the referenced group. This produced a NullPointerException (HTTP 500)\non analytics requests for any indicator using OUG{} over such an org unit, e.g.\n\n  GET /api/analytics.json?dimension=dx:\u003coug-indicator\u003e\u0026dimension=ou:LEVEL-3\u0026dimension=pe:2025\n\nA missing entry means a count of zero, not an error. Treat both a null map and a\nmissing group entry as zero, consistent with how analytics treats absent counts.\nThis also removes the prior \"Cannot find count\" throw, which likewise bubbled up\nas a 500 since getIndicatorValueObject does not catch it.\n\nPre-existing latent bug (the unguarded line dates to 2023); rare because it\nrequires an OUG{} indicator and an org unit whose subtree has zero matching\nmembers.\n\nCo-authored-by: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e","author":{"name":"Jason Pickering","email":"jason@dhis2.org"},"id":"957c053126bc4ecc25dba96679ca1091601a5682","tree_id":"34cb18e782878a03a13aa27aca94f8662ddc6bb3","timestamp":"2026-06-23T09:09:57Z","committer":{"name":"Jason Pickering","email":"jason@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/10954","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/repos","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/subscriptions"},"name":"dhis2-core","full_name":"dhis2/dhis2-core","description":"DHIS 2 Core